  "texts": [
    "On a dataset-specific basis, these features exhibit minimal or even adverse effects on the CoNLL 2003 dataset.",
    "However, they play a pivotal role in enhancing performance on scientific datasets.",
    "As discussed in § 3, LLMs are prone to integrating discussions about irrelevant scientific terms in their responses, a tendency less prevalent with general entities such as person names in the CoNLL dataset.",
    "Moreover, the encouragement for models to articulate responses in natural language proves more advantageous for scientific datasets, where entities tend to be more complex and varied.",
